Activity Bar


JoyClean — home cleaning robot (vacuum + mop + schedule cleaning via app).

JoyGuard — home security & patrol robot (cameras + alert + remote control).

JoyServe — restaurant service robot (deliver food from kitchen to table, obstacle avoidance).

JoyCheck — retail shelf checker (walk aisles, scan shelves, report missing stock or wrong pricing).

JoyMed — hospital helper (delivers meds, supplies, connects patients to doctors via video).


